The evidence with the title 'Raising the minimum wage to $12 by 2020 would lift wages for 35 ... ' says Jul 14, 2015  ... Over the phase - in period of the increases , affected workers would receive nearly $ 80 billion in increasedwages.Once the increase is fully phased-in, the average affected worker would earn roughly $ 2,300 more each year than she does today ( assuming no change in the number of work hours). 
